    "text": "Folie de Protecție PPF\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPachete & Prețuri\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nÎnfoliere Frontală (Zone expuse)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nInclude: capotă, bară față, aripi față, oglinzi\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nMașini mici\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nde la 5000 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n~ 8000 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nÎnfoliere Completă PPF\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nde la 15000 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nde la 17500 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nde la 19000 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFolie Protecție Parbriz (Exterior)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nOrice tip de autoturism\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDurată de viață: 1 an\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n1.200 RON\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n* Prețul final pentru pachetele PPF se stabilește după verificarea fizică a mașinii.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDacă îți dorești să păstrezi culoarea originală a mașinii, folia de protecție PPF este una dintre cele mai eficiente metode de protecție a caroseriei.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nServiciul de înfoliere cu folie de protecție PPF în Galați oferit de Vlad Detailing ajută la prevenirea deteriorării vopselei cauzate de pietricele, zgârieturi sau alți factori externi.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nBeneficiile foliei PPF:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPortofoliu\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nLucrări\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nColantări Auto\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nImaginile cu lucrări de colantare vor fi adăugate în curând.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nProtecție PPF\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nImaginile cu lucrări PPF vor fi adăugate în curând.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nVrei o schimbare sau protecție pentru mașina ta?\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nTe așt\nsrc-components-siteknowledge-generated-ts-62"
