    "id": "src-components-siteknowledge-generated-ts-90",
    "title": "src/components/siteKnowledge.generated.ts",
    "text": "Protejarea datelor cu caracter personal ale clienților și vizitatorilor site-ului reprezintă o prioritate pentru Vlad Detailing SRL. Această politică explică modul în care colectăm, utilizăm și protejăm informațiile furnizate de utilizatori.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPolitica se aplică tuturor utilizatorilor care accesează website-ul nostru, indiferent de dispozitivul utilizat (computer, telefon mobil, tabletă sau alte dispozitive conectate la internet).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPrelucrarea datelor se realizează în conformitate cu Regulamentul (UE) 2016/679 privind protecția datelor cu caracter personal (GDPR), aplicabil începând cu data de 25 mai 2018.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDatele personale pe care le putem colecta\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPentru desfășurarea activității și furnizarea serviciilor oferite, putem colecta anumite date personale, inclusiv:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnume și prenume;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nadresă de e-mail;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnumăr de telefon;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nadresă de domiciliu sau corespondență;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ninformații necesare pentru facturare;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nalte date furnizate voluntar prin formularele de contact sau programare.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nAceste informații sunt utilizate exclusiv pentru desfășurarea relației comerc\nsrc-components-siteknowledge-generated-ts-75"
