    "id": "src-components-siteknowledge-generated-ts-91",
    "title": "src/components/siteKnowledge.generated.ts",
    "text": "analizarea modului în care sunt utilizate serviciile oferite.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDatele nu vor fi utilizate în alte scopuri fără consimțământul persoanei vizate, cu excepția cazurilor prevăzute de lege.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPerioada de stocare a datelor\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDatele cu caracter personal sunt păstrate doar pe perioada necesară îndeplinirii scopurilor pentru care au fost colectate.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nDatele utilizate pentru facturare și evidență contabilă sunt arhivate conform legislației fiscale în vigoare, pentru o perioadă de minimum 10 ani.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nTransferul și divulgarea datelor\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nÎn mod normal, datele personale nu sunt transmise către terți.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nÎn anumite situații, acestea pot fi comunicate către:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nfurnizori de servicii IT;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nfurnizori de servicii contabile;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsultanți juridici;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nautorități publice, atunci când legea impune acest lucru.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nToți partenerii care prelucrează date în numele nostru sunt obligați să respecte cerințele privind protecția datelor personale.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nSecuritatea datelor\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nSocietatea noastră implementeaz\nsrc-components-siteknowledge-generated-ts-76"
